Meet the sisterly masterminds behind Vantage by MK, Muskaan and Kanishka! ✨

These Jaipur-based influencers aren’t just fashionistas, they’re the driving force behind this exciting sustainable clothing brand. Their passion for style goes beyond trends; it’s about empowering women through beautiful and ethical clothing.

Imagine their childhood years spent exploring the vibrant streets of Jaipur, soaking in the rich heritage and aesthetics of the Pink City. It’s no wonder their designs are infused with stunning vintage Indian florals and motifs, reimagined for the modern woman.

Vantage by MK isn’t just a brand; it’s a reflection of Muskaan and Kanishka’s creativity, their love for sustainable practices, and their desire to inspire you to dress with confidence and purpose.
